This report documents the comprehensive analysis of the PetStore FaaS application
deployed on AWS using Amplify. The analysis focused on identifying all API 
endpoints, authentication mechanisms, and generating a complete OpenAPI 3.0 
specification to guide the migration to IaaS (monolithic architecture).

